00:28:14.140 --> 00:28:15.460
there's definitely something wrong

00:28:15.460 --> 00:28:16.420
with this sentence.

00:28:16.420 --> 00:28:17.390
Think about it carefully.

00:28:17.460 --> 00:28:18.300
Isn't it?

00:28:18.360 --> 00:28:19.300
Indeed.

00:28:19.900 --> 00:28:22.590
If it's just the kind of family matters
that are hard to talk about,

00:28:22.740 --> 00:28:24.900
he could simply say
it's inconvenient to visit.

00:28:25.220 --> 00:28:26.340
There is someone at home.

00:28:26.700 --> 00:28:28.060
This sentence sounds odd.

00:28:28.220 --> 00:28:30.300
It's like someone is keeping watch
over his family.

00:28:31.180 --> 00:28:33.020
Did Prince Zhao kidnap his family

00:28:33.080 --> 00:28:34.660
and force him to be an undercover agent?

00:28:34.900 --> 00:28:36.680
My grandmother and I watched it
in the drama.

00:28:36.680 --> 00:28:37.880
It was always played like that.

00:28:39.700 --> 00:28:40.540
Yes.

00:28:55.300 --> 00:28:56.820
Lady Shen, you're looking for me.

00:29:01.580 --> 00:29:02.420
Lady Shen.

00:29:08.180 --> 00:29:09.020
Lady Shen.

00:29:11.020 --> 00:29:11.940
It's so dark.

00:29:13.620 --> 00:29:14.860
Why don't you turn on the light?

00:29:25.700 --> 00:29:26.620
Happy Birthday!

00:29:26.620 --> 00:29:27.460
Who is it?

00:29:31.660 --> 00:29:32.500
What's in his hand?

00:29:33.180 --> 00:29:34.020
It's a knife.

00:29:34.540 --> 00:29:35.380
It's a knife.

00:29:35.780 --> 00:29:36.620
Oh no!

00:29:36.780 --> 00:29:37.740
It's getting worse.

00:29:38.260 --> 00:29:39.300
He is driven to a dead end.

00:29:39.500 --> 00:29:40.940
Grandpa, Grandma,

00:29:40.940 --> 00:29:42.460
Father, Auntie,

00:29:42.460 --> 00:29:43.340
I'm scared.

00:29:43.580 --> 00:29:45.000
Don't be afraid, Yangyang.

00:29:45.000 --> 00:29:47.150
You close your eyes
before blowing out the candles.

00:29:47.160 --> 00:29:47.780
Close your eyes.

00:29:47.780 --> 00:29:49.190
Then you will not be afraid anymore.

00:29:53.780 --> 00:29:55.540
Yu San, you are really thoughtful.

00:29:55.550 --> 00:29:57.820
You guessed that we were going
to celebrate your birthday

00:29:57.830 --> 00:29:59.990
and even specially prepared a knife
to cut the cake.

00:30:02.740 --> 00:30:03.740
That's amazing.

00:30:03.740 --> 00:30:04.580
Here.

00:30:04.770 --> 00:30:05.660
Come on, cut the cake.

00:30:05.660 --> 00:30:06.580
Time to cut the cake.

00:30:08.380 --> 00:30:09.620
Come cut the cake, cut the cake.

00:30:12.540 --> 00:30:13.540
Yes.

00:30:13.540 --> 00:30:14.380
OK.

00:30:14.740 --> 00:30:17.780
- Happy Birthday.
- Happy Birthday.

00:30:20.300 --> 00:30:21.600
San, do you still remember

00:30:21.600 --> 00:30:23.730
you filled in your birthday
on your first day at work.

00:30:23.740 --> 00:30:24.800
It's just today, isn't it?

00:30:25.020 --> 00:30:26.660
Your parents aren't around.

00:30:26.660 --> 00:30:28.240
And there's no one helping you with it.

00:30:28.260 --> 00:30:29.660
So we took the liberty

00:30:29.800 --> 00:30:31.240
to celebrated your birthday for you.

00:30:31.820 --> 00:30:32.660
That's right.

00:30:41.940 --> 00:30:42.780
Yu San,

00:30:42.940 --> 00:30:44.380
actually,

00:30:44.380 --> 00:30:46.580
your age is about the same

00:30:46.740 --> 00:30:47.740
as Gongcai and Jicai.

00:30:47.740 --> 00:30:48.740
In our eyes,

00:30:48.940 --> 00:30:50.380
you are just a child.

00:30:50.660 --> 00:30:51.820
A child of our own family.

00:30:52.660 --> 00:30:54.140
- Yes.
- That's right.

00:30:54.140 --> 00:30:55.580
This birthday cake

00:30:56.020 --> 00:30:57.740
is a custom from our hometown.

00:30:58.060 --> 00:30:59.700
So, Yu San,

00:30:59.700 --> 00:31:00.900
don't despise it.

00:31:00.900 --> 00:31:01.800
- Don't mind.
- Yeah.

00:31:02.540 --> 00:31:03.500
Don't despise it.

00:31:05.100 --> 00:31:06.620
Actually, you've known about it, right?

00:31:10.400 --> 00:31:12.440
That's why your behavior
has been so strange lately.

00:31:13.220 --> 00:31:15.140
Isn't it?

00:31:15.140 --> 00:31:16.390
- Don't be impulsive.
- Speak.

00:31:16.390 --> 00:31:17.060
Isn't it?

00:31:17.300 --> 00:31:18.220
Isn't it? Isn't it?

00:31:18.220 --> 00:31:19.180
Don't...

00:31:19.180 --> 00:31:20.880
- Don't be impulsive.
- Don't be impulsive.

00:31:21.300 --> 00:31:22.500
Don't be impulsive. Don't.

00:31:22.870 --> 00:31:24.260
Yu San, don't be impulsive.

00:31:24.260 --> 00:31:25.980
- Don't be impulsive.
- Don't be afraid, Deyuan.

00:31:27.260 --> 00:31:28.980
Deyuan is just a servant girl.

00:31:30.140 --> 00:31:31.460
You're masters.

00:31:32.780 --> 00:31:34.180
You protect her like this?

00:31:34.620 --> 00:31:35.740
Deyuan is not a servant.

00:31:35.740 --> 00:31:36.580
She's our family.

00:31:37.160 --> 00:31:38.140
We went to great lengths

00:31:38.140 --> 00:31:39.260
to retrieve her slave deed,

00:31:39.260 --> 00:31:40.740
just so she could be a real person.

00:31:41.800 --> 00:31:42.820
That's just your way

00:31:42.820 --> 00:31:44.300
of winning people's hearts.

00:31:46.000 --> 00:31:47.760
Someone once said they wanted
to redeem me.

00:31:48.420 --> 00:31:49.380
But in the end,

00:31:50.020 --> 00:31:51.620
they still held my slave deed

00:31:54.500 --> 00:31:55.820
and used my family to threaten me.

00:31:58.180 --> 00:31:59.460
- Mother.
- Grandma.

00:31:59.460 --> 00:32:00.300
Grandma.

00:32:01.460 --> 00:32:02.300
Feng...

00:32:05.380 --> 00:32:06.220
San,

00:32:06.940 --> 00:32:08.260
no matter who has deceived you,

00:32:08.940 --> 00:32:10.660
but we are just ourselves.

00:32:11.090 --> 00:32:12.220
If you've been deceived once,

00:32:12.440 --> 00:32:13.740
you should walk away immediately,

00:32:13.940 --> 00:32:14.820
rather than doubt

00:32:14.820 --> 00:32:15.980
those around you.

00:32:17.020 --> 00:32:17.860
Do you know?

00:32:28.900 --> 00:32:29.900
You don't kill me?

00:32:32.470 --> 00:32:33.310
I...

00:32:33.900 --> 00:32:35.380
I am just a slave.

00:32:39.180 --> 00:32:40.540
Even though you kill me,

00:32:43.620 --> 00:32:45.260
nothing will happen to you.

00:32:46.340 --> 00:32:47.180
Yu San,

00:32:50.420 --> 00:32:52.020
you were holding this knife just now.

00:32:52.860 --> 00:32:53.700
I can see

00:32:54.140 --> 00:32:55.820
that you didn't truly intend to harm us.

00:32:56.500 --> 00:32:58.780
This shows that your conscience
has not been extinguished.

00:33:00.000 --> 00:33:02.140
If someone is truly behind you
trying to threaten you,

00:33:02.140 --> 00:33:02.980
you should choose

00:33:02.980 --> 00:33:04.980
to stand with us to deal with him,

00:33:05.490 --> 00:33:06.340
instead

00:33:06.340 --> 00:33:08.380
of risking your young life.

00:33:15.340 --> 00:33:16.680
You were the one who told them

00:33:16.680 --> 00:33:18.400
about the plan to infiltrate Yunlai,
right?

00:33:20.060 --> 00:33:21.180
Who's threatening you?

00:33:21.460 --> 00:33:22.500
Is it Prince Zhao?

00:33:25.540 --> 00:33:26.380
Yu San.

00:33:26.580 --> 00:33:27.420
Yu San.

00:33:28.020 --> 00:33:29.540
I used to work at Yunlai before.

00:33:29.860 --> 00:33:31.780
I know what kind of people they are.

00:33:32.400 --> 00:33:33.860
It must have been very tough, right?

00:33:34.380 --> 00:33:35.220
Look at me.

00:33:35.610 --> 00:33:36.460
Me.

00:33:36.460 --> 00:33:38.100
I am Handsome Shen.

00:33:38.100 --> 00:33:39.900
You must have heard of my name, right?

00:33:40.420 --> 00:33:41.240
This person

00:33:41.240 --> 00:33:42.780
is the top chef of Juxian Alley.

00:33:42.780 --> 00:33:44.100
You've heard of this title, huh?

00:33:44.220 --> 00:33:45.200
And Mr. Lin.

00:33:45.480 --> 00:33:46.580
Vice Prefect Lin.

00:33:46.580 --> 00:33:48.180
He is the upright magistrate.

00:33:48.180 --> 00:33:49.880
You've surely heard
of his title even more.

00:33:50.020 --> 00:33:51.960
Can he still not resolve the matter
behind you?

00:33:52.260 --> 00:33:53.000
Sticking with us

00:33:53.020 --> 00:33:54.690
is definitely better
than being with them.

00:33:54.700 --> 00:33:55.350
Isn't it?

00:33:56.420 --> 00:33:58.300
I remember you once said

00:33:58.440 --> 00:33:59.580
you're a slave.

00:34:00.340 --> 00:34:01.700
But you have to trust us

00:34:01.700 --> 00:34:03.100
that we will surely find a way

00:34:03.100 --> 00:34:04.420
to help you solve this problem.

00:34:04.700 --> 00:34:06.200
If money can solve this problem,

00:34:06.200 --> 00:34:07.320
we'll spend whatever it takes

00:34:07.320 --> 00:34:08.440
and exert our utmost effort;

00:34:08.440 --> 00:34:09.860
if money can't solve it,

00:34:09.860 --> 00:34:11.260
we'll still find a way.

00:34:12.020 --> 00:34:13.660
Can you trust us?

00:34:22.200 --> 00:34:23.340
Can you

00:34:24.320 --> 00:34:25.360
swear?

00:34:26.020 --> 00:34:26.860
We can.

00:34:27.150 --> 00:34:28.410
- We can.
- We can.

00:34:29.380 --> 00:34:30.220
We swear.

00:34:30.420 --> 00:34:31.260
We swear.

00:34:43.340 --> 00:34:46.260
It was I who betrayed Mr. Lin
and Mr. Shen.

00:34:47.460 --> 00:34:49.340
I'm afraid that if I make no progress,

00:34:52.700 --> 00:34:55.140
they will kill my father and mother.

00:34:56.840 --> 00:34:58.500
I have wronged you.

00:34:59.790 --> 00:35:01.900
I am a spy from Prince Zhao.

00:35:05.860 --> 00:35:06.700
I don't deserve...

00:35:07.460 --> 00:35:09.340
I don't deserve to be treated
like this by you.

00:35:11.380 --> 00:35:12.220
Sorry.

00:35:14.420 --> 00:35:15.300
Sorry.

00:35:16.540 --> 00:35:17.420
San.

00:35:17.420 --> 00:35:18.260
It's fine.

00:35:19.000 --> 00:35:20.020
It's all in the past now.

00:35:20.300 --> 00:35:21.620
It's over. It's fine now.

00:35:23.700 --> 00:35:26.740
(Prince Zhao's Mansion)

00:35:38.740 --> 00:35:40.250
What are you still standing there for?

00:35:40.460 --> 00:35:41.300
Drink it.

00:35:55.060 --> 00:35:56.300
You've had your tea.

00:35:57.140 --> 00:35:58.340
Say

00:35:58.340 --> 00:35:59.260
what you want directly.

00:36:04.020 --> 00:36:06.300
Lu Yun has already transferred out

00:36:06.360 --> 00:36:08.480
all the salt and iron
we were going to use in advance.

00:36:09.220 --> 00:36:10.820
Lin Anran hasn't found anything either.

00:36:11.620 --> 00:36:12.460
But

00:36:12.980 --> 00:36:14.220
Yunlai

00:36:14.740 --> 00:36:16.180
is no longer safe.

00:36:17.060 --> 00:36:19.100
However, rather than abandoning Yunlai,

00:36:21.780 --> 00:36:23.260
it would be better to kill Lin Yan.

00:36:23.900 --> 00:36:25.120
One finished, all is finished.

00:36:32.620 --> 00:36:34.780
Lin Yan would even oppose us
for the Shen family.

00:36:34.800 --> 00:36:36.360
If he finds out about the Cui family...

00:36:40.060 --> 00:36:41.620
Since you can't make up your mind,

00:36:44.180 --> 00:36:45.820
I'll make the decision for you.

00:36:48.140 --> 00:36:48.980
Stop.

00:36:51.220 --> 00:36:53.220
Why are you still acting so impulsively?

00:36:54.420 --> 00:36:55.260
It's easy to do.

00:36:55.260 --> 00:36:56.180
What about wrapping up?

00:36:57.420 --> 00:36:58.540
He's a Rank III official

00:36:58.540 --> 00:36:59.540
in Yong'an.

00:36:59.540 --> 00:37:00.980
You think you can easily kill him?

00:37:03.500 --> 00:37:04.420
In the final analysis,

00:37:05.940 --> 00:37:07.620
you misjudged Lin Yan.

00:37:10.620 --> 00:37:12.740
You thought he had long since
let go of the past,

00:37:12.800 --> 00:37:15.060
and that as long as he could live well,
it would be fine.

00:37:15.060 --> 00:37:16.980
But little do you know
he has his own plans.

00:37:18.300 --> 00:37:19.820
It was precisely because you projected

00:37:19.820 --> 00:37:21.260
your longing for my brother
onto him

00:37:21.260 --> 00:37:22.300
and insisted on keeping him

00:37:22.300 --> 00:37:23.840
that today's disaster was brought about.

00:37:23.840 --> 00:37:24.580
Shut up!

00:37:27.420 --> 00:37:29.660
I was worried too much,

00:37:29.660 --> 00:37:30.980
so I spoke out of turn.

00:37:31.420 --> 00:37:32.580
Please forgive me, Father.

00:37:35.620 --> 00:37:36.620
I tell you,

00:37:38.380 --> 00:37:40.820
killing would cause unnecessary trouble.

00:37:41.420 --> 00:37:42.700
His current location

00:37:43.420 --> 00:37:44.940
is too close to His Majesty.

00:37:45.780 --> 00:37:47.260
What we can do is to make him fall,

00:37:47.880 --> 00:37:48.780
falling into a position

00:37:48.790 --> 00:37:50.420
where his words don't count.

00:37:50.660 --> 00:37:51.500
Only then

00:37:51.940 --> 00:37:53.420
can you do whatever you want.

00:37:53.860 --> 00:37:55.140
Rein in your temper.

00:37:55.740 --> 00:37:56.860
Think more.

00:37:57.900 --> 00:37:58.740
Yes.

00:38:02.820 --> 00:38:04.580
(Xuanzheng Gate)

00:38:04.600 --> 00:38:06.820
Mr. Lin, you probably never expected

00:38:07.410 --> 00:38:09.820
that one day the Appeal Drum

00:38:09.980 --> 00:38:11.780
would be sounded against yourself.

00:38:13.940 --> 00:38:14.780
Your Majesty,

00:38:15.620 --> 00:38:17.550
a good citizen from the Western Market,
Feng Li,

00:38:17.560 --> 00:38:19.300
has accused Lin Yan, the Vice Prefect,

00:38:19.300 --> 00:38:21.550
of colluding with Cao Rong,
the Vice Minister of Justice,

00:38:21.560 --> 00:38:23.070
to coerce a confession through torture

00:38:23.080 --> 00:38:24.260
and render an unjust judgment.

00:38:24.260 --> 00:38:26.700
Feng Li, willing to offend the superior,

00:38:26.700 --> 00:38:28.040
subjected to corporal punishment,

00:38:28.280 --> 00:38:29.720
still seeks to redress the injustice.

00:38:46.660 --> 00:38:48.660
(Submitted by Censor Luo Zhi)

00:38:50.420 --> 00:38:51.490
How do you

00:38:51.830 --> 00:38:52.900
explain this?

00:38:54.660 --> 00:38:55.500
Your Majesty,

00:38:55.560 --> 00:38:57.330
Feng Li poisoned the Shen family's
restaurant

00:38:57.330 --> 00:38:58.620
on Juxian Alley last year.

00:38:58.620 --> 00:39:00.220
The Shen family and I are cousins.

00:39:00.220 --> 00:39:01.200
Thus, upon hearing this,

00:39:01.220 --> 00:39:02.780
in strict accordance with the Six Codes,

00:39:03.000 --> 00:39:05.260
and submitted it
to the Ministry of Justice for judgment.

00:39:05.270 --> 00:39:07.080
How could I join hands
with Vice Minister Cao?

00:39:08.660 --> 00:39:09.500
Your Majesty,

00:39:10.420 --> 00:39:12.300
in this case, both testimonial

00:39:12.300 --> 00:39:13.630
and physical evidence are present,

00:39:13.660 --> 00:39:16.020
and the judgment is rendered
strictly according to the law.

00:39:16.220 --> 00:39:17.080
Therefore,

00:39:17.080 --> 00:39:19.860
Feng Li fled in fear of punishment.

00:39:20.540 --> 00:39:22.300
Since Feng Li has retreated to Yong'an

00:39:22.660 --> 00:39:24.600
and has connected with you,

00:39:24.630 --> 00:39:26.260
why have you not
handed over the criminal

00:39:26.260 --> 00:39:28.460
to the authorities,

00:39:28.460 --> 00:39:32.020
but instead allowed him
to falsely accuse Vice Prefect Lin?

00:39:32.460 --> 00:39:34.540
What is your true intention?

00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:37.220
It's a minor dispute between merchants
in the Western Market.

00:39:37.220 --> 00:39:39.580
If it weren't for Mr. Lin mediating
between them,

00:39:39.700 --> 00:39:41.220
how could it bypass the Market Office

00:39:41.700 --> 00:39:43.140
and reach the Ministry of Justice?

00:39:43.620 --> 00:39:46.220
Could it be that you are protecting them

00:39:46.590 --> 00:39:49.500
just because the person involved
is a relative?

00:39:51.150 --> 00:39:52.500
Western Market is a prime location.

00:39:52.500 --> 00:39:53.680
Poisoning is a serious matter.

00:39:53.680 --> 00:39:55.280
How could it be considered a minor case?

00:39:55.620 --> 00:39:58.220
It used to be under the jurisdiction
of the Market Office.

00:39:58.580 --> 00:40:00.300
The Western Market was a complete mess.

00:40:00.500 --> 00:40:01.980
After this case was heavily sentenced,

00:40:02.500 --> 00:40:03.700
those merchants

00:40:03.700 --> 00:40:05.700
became much more orderly.

00:40:07.060 --> 00:40:08.140
How many errands

00:40:08.460 --> 00:40:11.100
has Capital Prefecture handled
beyond the Market Office?

00:40:11.120 --> 00:40:12.460
So mighty.

00:40:13.300 --> 00:40:14.460
I also heard

00:40:14.660 --> 00:40:16.500
the Lantern Festival had not yet ended

00:40:16.500 --> 00:40:18.860
when the Prefecture ordered people
to be on duty

00:40:19.180 --> 00:40:22.340
and even encouraged the people
to beat the Appeal Drum.

00:40:22.500 --> 00:40:23.760
The common people in the capital

00:40:24.220 --> 00:40:25.140
now

00:40:25.340 --> 00:40:26.900
only trust the Capital Prefecture.

00:40:26.900 --> 00:40:28.420
Perhaps, in their eyes,

00:40:28.560 --> 00:40:30.540
even if it were personally judged
by His Majesty,

00:40:31.340 --> 00:40:32.580
it would not compare

00:40:33.000 --> 00:40:34.920
to a single word from Mr. Lin.

00:40:51.020 --> 00:40:56.300
(Shaoguang's Food Notes
Spring Outing Painting)

00:40:56.300 --> 00:41:01.260
(Four poems and four dishes
for the four seasons)

00:41:31.100 --> 00:41:33.310
Shadows pair up under moonlight

00:41:33.590 --> 00:41:36.120
Surrounding the stove's fire

00:41:36.120 --> 00:41:40.730
Red beans sown for longing

00:41:41.040 --> 00:41:43.900
Heart ablaze, cooling sorrow

00:41:43.900 --> 00:41:45.830
At a glance

00:41:45.830 --> 00:41:49.900
Cheeks blush with red

00:41:50.970 --> 00:41:53.490
Cooking smoke fading behind the house

00:41:53.490 --> 00:41:56.230
Longing boils, fierce at the taste

00:41:56.430 --> 00:42:01.080
It's okay for snow to stop me

00:42:01.080 --> 00:42:03.590
I'll brew a jug of new wine

00:42:03.590 --> 00:42:09.800
Getting drunk as time goes by

00:42:11.120 --> 00:42:16.440
Enjoy the endless world to the fullest

00:42:16.710 --> 00:42:18.970
Swallowing everything

00:42:19.210 --> 00:42:21.540
Time will tell

00:42:22.030 --> 00:42:26.550
Don't let true feelings wait in vain

00:42:26.550 --> 00:42:30.530
Meetings seem but an illusion

00:42:31.140 --> 00:42:36.190
Enjoy the endless world to the fullest

00:42:36.450 --> 00:42:40.740
Leave the worries to the future

00:42:41.060 --> 00:42:43.610
Can we not plan

00:42:43.610 --> 00:42:46.160
Not hope, not look back

00:42:46.160 --> 00:42:51.410
Focus on today, neglecting the results

00:42:51.930 --> 00:42:54.040
I understand
the furrowed brows of doubt

